reparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Jakarta Activation API 2.0.0 moved from javax.activation to jakarta.activation and the API jar alone omits com.sun.activation registry implementation classes needed by normal CommandMap, FileTypeMap, MimetypesFileTypeMap, and DataHandler usage.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"com.sun.activation:jakarta.activation:2.0.0\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"The jakarta.activation-api:2.0.0 jar is documented as API-only and its classes reference com.sun.activation.registries classes that are not packaged in the API jar. The companion com.sun.activation:jakarta.activation:2.0.0 implementation jar provides those registry classes and enables meaningful coverage of default MIME type and mailcap command-map behavior.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Use jakarta.activation.* imports for 2.0.0 tests; do not keep the existing javax.activation imports. Be careful with global one-shot/static Activation state such as DataHandler.setDataContentHandlerFactory, CommandMap.setDefaultCommandMap, and FileTypeMap.setDefaultFileTypeMap; prefer local instances or isolate such assertions to avoid cross-test contamination.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"com.sun.activation:jakarta.activation:2.0.0 also contains jakarta.activation API classes, so Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative for classpath behavior.\",\n    \"Do not substitute org.eclipse.angus:angus-activation for this 2.0.0 case; it does not provide the same public com.sun.activation.registries compatibility needed by the 2.0.0 API classes.\",\n    \"Existing 1.2.1 tests are namespace-incompatible with 2.0.0 and will continue to fail javac until migrated from javax.activation to jakarta.activation.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ef1f80accb2e63f016a41bd1fa19c81958a411fa3401ad93c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1265, "output": 1191, "cacheRead": 32256, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34712, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782693139210, "responseId": "resp_0ef1f80accb2e63f016a41bd13cebc819582c6d66c5306da87"}}
